text: Jack Frackleton (born February 14, 1959) is an American rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1959 births Category:Living people Category:American male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
